## Decisions Made

- Project scope is confirmed as: **design and implement one complete APT-style attack
  simulation scenario in CITEF**, not a full platform build.
- The Cyber Range team handles infrastructure and platform development; the capstone
  team contributes the scenario content and simulation tooling.
- Scattered Spider is the leading APT candidate based on its well-documented TTPs,
  lack of zero-day requirements, and relevance to current threat landscape.

